                ዘለለ፡ ዕለት። ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ሶበ፡ ኀልቀ፡ ሲሳየ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ተንሥአ፡ ወሖረ፡ ይስእላ፡ ለሥዕለ።</incipit>
              <note>Twenty-Two Miracles of Abunä Täklä Haymanot to be read on the day observing the
                translation of his body, Gǝnbot 12</note>
            </msItem>
